00:12:31.630 --> 00:12:34.660
As Mari said a little bit about,

00:12:34.660 --> 00:12:37.970
we exist through a
tri-partite agreement.

00:12:37.970 --> 00:12:40.040
The National Park Services,
where I am based,

00:12:40.040 --> 00:12:42.580
we administer and run the programs.

00:12:42.580 --> 00:12:46.310 position:56%
The American Institute of Architects
advises our professionalism

00:12:46.310 --> 00:12:49.850
and makes recommendations for
documentation, and we're here

00:12:49.850 --> 00:12:51.610
in the Library of Congress,
which preserves

00:12:51.610 --> 00:12:53.490
and distributes our records.

00:12:53.490 --> 00:12:58.560
It was made permanent and validated
in 1935 by the Historic Sites Act

00:12:58.560 --> 00:13:01.620
as a regular duty of
the federal government.

00:13:01.620 --> 00:13:04.360
The architects and landscape
architects employed during the

00:13:04.360 --> 00:13:07.720
