document, a folly, a garden house,

00:15:23.090 --> 00:15:27.030 position:56%
a summer, this great sort of Chinese
Chippendale little summer house

00:15:27.030 --> 00:15:28.330
and a garden.

00:15:28.330 --> 00:15:30.310
Beautiful photograph and
beautiful drawings, should you want

00:15:30.310 --> 00:15:33.470 position:56%
to build one in your own background.

00:15:33.470 --> 00:15:35.910
I was always impressed by
this early set of drawings

00:15:35.910 --> 00:15:38.070
of the Beau Caray in New Orleans.

00:15:38.070 --> 00:15:42.110
That is a comprehensive measure
drawing of one entire square block,

00:15:42.110 --> 00:15:45.220
every detail there, and then
the elevations of the structures

00:15:45.220 --> 00:15:47.870
that make up the block
from the outside.

00:15:47.870 --> 00:15:49.330
Cover a little bit
of geography here.

00:15:49.330 --> 00:15:52.200
They were in Acoma in New Mexico.

00:15:52.200 --> 00:15:55.990
Many, many drawings of
the great old pueblo.

00:15:55.990 --> 00:15:58.230
You'll see a great aerial
photograph of the pueblo,

00:15:58.230 --> 00:16:02.010
and there's just the first
