historical landscape architecture.

00:16:16.190 --> 00:16:17.690
When I first joined the program --

00:16:17.690 --> 00:16:20.060
I also have a degree in
landscape architecture --

00:16:20.060 --> 00:16:24.100
I was asked to run a series of
pilot projects that would look

00:16:24.100 --> 00:16:27.290 position:56%
