architecture than architecture,

00:16:27.290 --> 00:16:30.190
what is so different when an
architect looks at something

00:16:30.190 --> 00:16:33.070
versus a landscape architect,
so we were asked to do a number

00:16:33.070 --> 00:16:35.170
of pilot projects in the 70s.

00:16:35.170 --> 00:16:38.960
The first major one was actually
