00:32:27.060 --> 00:32:30.210
It's 160 feet across
the base of that tree.

00:32:30.210 --> 00:32:33.360
Sadly, it was hit by a car
and I believe lightning

00:32:33.360 --> 00:32:35.730
and has since been removed.

00:32:35.730 --> 00:32:37.030
&gt;&gt; Oh.

00:32:37.030 --> 00:32:38.330
&gt;&gt; Paul Dolinsky: See, that's
