00:35:06.990 --> 00:35:11.100
It's now on the opposite
side of Independence Avenue.

00:35:11.100 --> 00:35:15.510
The remaining Zelkova is a truly
unique specimen on the Mall,

00:35:15.510 --> 00:35:16.810
as you can see by the photos.

00:35:16.810 --> 00:35:18.760
I really would encourage
you to walk down and see it.

00:35:18.760 --> 00:35:22.290
It's sort of right before the
street where the cross-street is

00:35:22.290 --> 00:35:25.850
for the Native American Museum,
